1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,791
In the morning when I woke up and wanted to go to the toilets

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:08,541
They allowed me to go there to relieve myself and return

3
00:00:09,083 --> 00:00:12,791
And as for bathing, it was twice a week

4
00:00:13,625 --> 00:00:16,250
On Mondays and Thursdays we had the right to bathe

5
00:00:16,875 --> 00:00:20,083
And they gave us ten minutes or a quarter hour to bathe

6
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,500
Interviewer: When you relieved yourself, did you do so comfortably?

7
00:00:26,500 --> 00:00:28,125
Or did you feel you were being watched?

8
00:00:30,791 --> 00:00:33,791
When I entered the toilets, I felt I was being watched

9
00:00:34,500 --> 00:00:37,000
Interviewer: And were you actually watched, or was it just a feeling?

10
00:00:37,041 --> 00:00:38,083
It was a feeling

11
00:00:38,125 --> 00:00:40,041
Interviewer: So you weren’t watched?
Witness: No, I wasn’t watched

12
00:00:40,041 --> 00:00:42,541
But it was my feeling because the toilets were adjacent to the prison

13
00:00:43,375 --> 00:00:48,041
It was next to the parking area, and the jailer stood outside next to the toilets

14
00:00:48,875 --> 00:00:51,750
Interviewer: Regarding cleanliness in the prison

15
00:00:51,791 --> 00:00:54,041
Did they give you cleaning supplies to clean the room?

16
00:00:54,083 --> 00:00:56,916
Yes, they gave us some

17
00:00:57,416 --> 00:00:59,041
Interviewer: Were they available regularly?

18
00:00:59,083 --> 00:01:02,000
Yes, available—they gave us Dettol and a bucket of water

19
00:01:03,375 --> 00:01:05,375
Every two days we wiped the room

20
00:01:06,041 --> 00:01:11,375
Interviewer: Was the cleaning time mandatory on a certain day?

21
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:14,625
Every two days we had the task of cleaning the room

22
00:01:14,958 --> 00:01:16,083
We did the cleaning inside the room

23
00:01:17,041 --> 00:01:20,750
Interviewer: Was hot and cold water available in the showers?

24
00:01:20,750 --> 00:01:23,250
Yes, they heated the water for us to bathe with

25
00:01:23,250 --> 00:01:28,125
They gave us a bucket of water with about 50 liters of water

26
00:01:28,791 --> 00:01:32,416
We bathed with it—we had to finish within 10 minutes to a quarter hour

27
00:01:32,666 --> 00:01:35,250
Interviewer: Did they distribute underwear to you?
Witness: No

28
00:01:36,541 --> 00:01:38,750
Interviewer: Didn’t they give you other clothes?
Witness: No

29
00:01:40,125 --> 00:01:43,375
When I sent them to bring me the medicine

30
00:01:43,666 --> 00:01:47,750
My family sent me underwear and pajamas

31
00:01:48,875 --> 00:01:50,750
Interviewer: Was bringing them in normal?
Witness: Yes

32
00:01:51,666 --> 00:01:53,375
Interviewer: Did they not allow visits in the prison?

33
00:01:53,416 --> 00:01:57,291
No, they didn’t allow anyone to do that, and my family knew that
